<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Memory Matrix: Icons of Computing</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/styles.css">
        
    </head>
    <body>
<div id="confetti-container"></div>
<header>
    <h1>Memory Matrix</h1>
    <h2>Icons of Computing</h2>
    <p style="padding-top: 15px; font-size: .8em;">Made with ❤️ in <a href="https://vscodeedu.com">Visual Studio Code for Education</a></p>
    <div id="timer" aria-label="Game timer"></div>
    <div id="match-info" aria-label="Match information"></div>
</header>
<main>
    <p>In this game, click on two squares to find matching symbols.<br>Try to find all the matching pairs in the grid. Good luck!</p>
    <div id="congratulations">Congratulations! You found all the pairs!</div>        
    <button id="play-again" style="display: none;">Play Again</button>
    
</main>

    </body>
</html>
